cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper deals with scene understanding problems such as predicting the pose of 3D objects, inferring street crossings of pedestrians, etc. These are all problems related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces techniques for speeding up inference, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of simulation software and computer graphics also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the graphics (cs.GR) or robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
